## 6. Default Credentials

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Username** | `admin` |
| **Password** | `admin123` |

> [!CAUTION]
> Change the default password before sharing or deploying the application on any network.
>
> To change the admin password, run:
> ```python
> import bcrypt, mysql.connector
> new_pw = b"YourNewSecurePassword"
> h = bcrypt.hashpw(new_pw, bcrypt.gensalt()).decode()
> cn = mysql.connector.connect(host='localhost', user='root', password='', database='smart_attendance_db')
> cur = cn.cursor()
> cur.execute('UPDATE admin_users SET password_hash = %s WHERE username = %s', (h, 'admin'))
> cn.commit()
> cn.close()
> ```

