## 8. Restarting the Server Later

After initial setup is complete, starting the server on future uses only needs these two steps:

```powershell
# Step 1 — Make sure XAMPP MySQL is running (XAMPP Control Panel)

# Step 2 — Start Flask from the project directory
.\venv\Scripts\python.exe app.py
```

Then navigate to: **`http://127.0.0.1:5000`**

